com.mewna.catnip.util.logging

Interface LogAdapter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultLogAdapter

    public interface LogAdapter
    If, for some reason, you want to plug in your own logging framework that ISN'T logback, SLF4J, ..., then you can implement this interface. Check out DefaultLogAdapter for an example.
    Since:
    9/3/18.
    Author:
    amy
